title: My Todos
message:
Today was quite busy.

I had to commit my project to Git and upload a photo on the college portal so it could be verified and published. I was a bit nervous, but I double-checked everything and got it done.

After that,

I made sure to leave class on time because I wanted to see Yamuna at the bus stop. She usually waits near Kovilpatti's busses, and the bus doesn't wait long.

title: At Last
message:
Today was amazing!

I've had a crush on Karthik in Mech class for a long time. Today, I finally got the courage to tell him. I was so nervous, but I did it!

To my surprise, he said he liked me too! We spent the rest of the day talking and laughing. I can't believe it!

I feel like the happiest girl in the world. I keep thinking about him and our future together. I can't wait to see what happens next!

title: Me and Karthik Work Together
description: We both worked as IT Team, SafeGuarded the code
message:
Today was quite a day!

Karthik and I both ended up working on the IT team for the campus event. It was a bit of a mix-up, but it turned out to be great. Karthik created an awesome automation script to send out emails to everyone, which made everything run so smoothly.

Even though we were both surprised by how we ended up in IT, it was a lot of fun. The event was a success, and it felt good to be a part of it.

Here’s to more unexpected adventures!

And this is the script he wrote: https://github.com/CandleOil-Karthik/AutomateMail

title: My Portfolio
description: My New portfolio and Git Problems
message:
Today was a whirlwind of emotions.

I finally finished creating my new portfolio, and it's looking fantastically awesome—way better than my old one! I was so excited to share it, but then I hit a major snag.

I faced a critical bug while trying to push the code to Git. It was so frustrating, and it took me all day to figure out what was wrong. After a lot of troubleshooting, I had to use my Git access token to push the code successfully.

Here's the token I used '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'. I’m relieved that it’s finally done, and my portfolio is live now. What a day!

title: Personal
message:
Today was unexpected but interesting.

Yamuna and Diviya both proposed to me, not knowing the full truth about who I am.

Now you need to create another two private repositories for these two girls, similar to the others. Flag FoundTheGurl{DumpsGuyCode}
